org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.cache.persistence.pagemem

Class CheckpointMetricsTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.cache.persistence.pagemem.CheckpointMetricsTracker

  • public class CheckpointMetricsTracker
extends Object
    Tracks various checkpoint phases and stats. Assumed sequence of events:
    1. Checkpoint start
    2. CP Lock wait start
    3. CP mark start
    4. CP Lock release
    5. Pages write start
    6. fsync start
    7. Checkpoint end
